{"tid":443740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"經歷緊有生以黎最難捱一程車，你問我答","createTime":"2017-10-22T00:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T08:54:14.000Z","uid":5241,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"131d8b4b0a92bf7d7d5c7afcb29851bb4698cf48","tid":443740,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:22:00.000Z","msg":"由塞爾維亞belgrade搭去黑山kotor，需時十二個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n最淒涼係後面有兩個廢老勁大聲唱歌傾計仲大力拍手，已經三個幾鐘冇停過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n媽我想訓！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw唔敢叫佢地收聲驚佢地傷害我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ndata有限，盡覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133b3327869a2cd7cd732791d73efce60d38c462","tid":443740,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:25:09.000Z","msg":"岩岩俾佢踢親手，我綜開然後另一個廢老拍我同我舉姆指，做乜撚野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b133a151f6242aa8c9d4168571c25bfcc12b4e","tid":443740,"uid":57469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:25:19.000Z","msg":"樓主去歐洲backpack?"},{"pid":"61672b6ecfc402597ad869623447920e468f5c8a","tid":443740,"uid":5241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩俾佢踢親手，我<span style=\"color: red;\">縮</span>開然後另一個廢老拍我同我舉姆指，做乜撚野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"76fa2b0feb1c5732be889b56916d08def517657b","tid":443740,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:26:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主去歐洲backpack?</blockquote><br />\n拎左個20吋喼，應該唔算backpack<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8ffcc440a8583f4d9bafe30d5de1f72bfe08ba","tid":443740,"uid":5241,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:30:01.000Z","msg":"廢老a又拍我了，佢話要食煙叫我唔好講，我心諗你肯收嗲食屎都唔關我事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且我有得say no咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a588c092df9a319c5872aeb3a9a4e169a6543bc7","tid":443740,"uid":5241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:32:14.000Z","msg":"唉俾佢拍完覺得自己好污糟，好似俾人老強咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c814504dc19f53b7c4040989d2dcbd6907df80","tid":443740,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:32:16.000Z","msg":"影相拍片啦"},{"pid":"f8798e6a8c087a7ed60e7a4c4e4a72625e95827a","tid":443740,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影相拍片啦</blockquote><br />\n響歐洲拍黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜巴熄哂燈都影唔到"},{"pid":"2950b17cd6ca1083ec30ae91ce4d76757e79900e","tid":443740,"uid":67432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:38:49.000Z","msg":"東歐佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b18f55cd7f8833ffdfd20a7645037966a7f9bf2","tid":443740,"uid":16284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:41:29.000Z","msg":"果時係日本搭夜行巴士十粒鐘，雙人座位<br />\n<br />\n側邊果個口極臭，張開個口加鼻&quot;寒&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我戴住口罩忍左十粒鐘，果時冬天架車係開暖氣，果個焗束感真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f326d8040240c5e346da4b0597ef7c9d2a9bc585","tid":443740,"uid":5241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:42:35.000Z","msg":"廢老食完枝煙收撚左嗲，唔知係咪了左件心事就可以收皮。<br />\n<br />\n求佢地咪撚再嘈，樓主試下訓，希望唔會幾分鐘後就上水r你地傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b72fec93b1ac97ae52352b7f6aebfc50d82669","tid":443740,"uid":5241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果時係日本搭夜行巴士十粒鐘，雙人座位<br />\n<br />\n側邊果個口極臭，張開個口加鼻&quot;寒&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我戴住口罩忍左十粒鐘，果時冬天架車係開暖氣，果個焗束感真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好慘，嘈都可以戴個隔音好耳機隔一隔，鼻真係冇得塞撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2beaa3d7df04716e5c738c71a5b9170a4a3d921f","tid":443740,"uid":51478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:44:28.000Z","msg":"好慘 但好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f43352b2d2e42b966dd87212f88a2ecad99c59d","tid":443740,"uid":5241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T00:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好慘 但好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地個look好似啲道友阿叔，其實我好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\